cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.CY, cs.SE 

The paper deals with DDoS mitigation over a QKD network using software-defined networking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves network infrastructure and communication protocols, which suggests categories such as cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves cyber-physical systems, which suggests categories such as cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
